<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4693474>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 10. Distribution map of Chromocheilosia and Myolepta species in Chile: C. bicolor (Shannon & Aubertin, 1933) (pink circles); Chromocheilosia incerta (Shannon & Aubertin, 1933) (red circles); C. pubescens (Shannon & Aubertin, 1933) (light blue circles); M. haemorrhoidalis (Philippi, 1865) (green circles); Myolepta luctuosa (Bigot, 1857) (yellow circles), and M. nausicaa (Hull, 1937) (Brown circles)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4693474/files/figure.png" .
